---
Language: Cpp
BasedOnStyle: Google

# Formatting rules requested by the user:
# 1. Next line braces (Allman style)
BreakBeforeBraces: Allman

# 2. Train* style pointers (Pointer alignment to the left)
PointerAlignment: Left

# Other helpful adjustments for standard C++ conventions
IndentWidth: 4
ColumnLimit: 100
AllowShortFunctionsOnASingleLine: false
NamespaceIndentation: All
...
